
Step 1:
	- Open the terminal/command line and then go to the directory.
	- Type the command " nodemon server.js" (this command will start the backend server).
	- Now leave the terminal/command line window unclosed and open a new terminal/command-line window.
Step 2:
	- In the new terminal/command line window type the command "cd client" to enter into the client folder.
	- To start the app run the command "npm start".
